{"tid":1258492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退休後仍佔用警察宿舍近三年　警員遭入稟追討逾21萬租金","createTime":"2019-06-26T06:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T06:49:47.000Z","uid":257200,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0789d2691b41f31c702473ff151e7db79e0046fa","tid":1258492,"uid":257200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:44:03.000Z","msg":"一名警員於2016年8月退休後，未有按規定交回警察宿舍之單位，律政司長代表警務處長入稟區域法院，追討該名退休警員逾21萬元租金及利息，並交還宿舍單位。  入稟狀指，被告吳立斌與家人自2004年5月獲分配入住上水已婚警察宿舍，須於退休前休假後兩個月內，交還宿舍單位，否則需支付市值租金。但被告在2016年8月退休前休假後，至今一直佔用單位並沒有支付租金。  律政司長代表警務處長現向被告追討逾21萬元租金及利息，以及要求被告交還單位。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-26-2019/53905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-26-2019%2F53905&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=b645393c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-26-2019/53905</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市值租金 3年21萬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f15b463be6ed627d8572471c5dbfa94277cf11","tid":1258492,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"點樣可以住咁耐無人理"},{"pid":"02f13dfe2103529e9418b142688645a55f9216bb","tid":1258492,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0lFj3yffAQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0lFj3yffAQs&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=0e1875e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0lFj3yffAQs</a>"}]}